ition. Whether it's sharing educational resources, participating in awareness events, or supporting asthma research, each of us can make a difference in the lives of individuals living with asthma.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-497_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-498_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-499_">Conclusion</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/concept-of-asthma-on-rustic-wooden-table-2023-11-27-05-28-41-utc.jpg?v=1708446183" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/concept-of-asthma-on-rustic-wooden-table-2023-11-27-05-28-41-utc.jpg?v=1708446183 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/concept-of-asthma-on-rustic-wooden-table-2023-11-27-05-28-41-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1708446183 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/concept-of-asthma-on-rustic-wooden-table-2023-11-27-05-28-41-utc_500x.jpg?v=1708446183 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Educating for change: World Asthma Day and asthma education - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Educating for change: World Asthma Day and asthma education - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-501_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-502_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by AtlasComposer via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-504_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">World Asthma Day serves as a reminder of the importance of breathing easily and the challenges faced by those living with asthma. By dispelling myths, raising awareness, and supporting organisations dedicated to asthma education and advocacy, we can work together to ensure that everyone affected by asthma receives the care and sup